y, and options, Todoist strips much of that away to offer a clean, modern, and fairly simple to use to-do list system.\n\nLabels give you a way of tagging your tasks to add another layer of organization.\n\nOne of the more unique features of Todoist is its use of natural language processing. Create a new task and enter Complete new logo by tomorrow at 2pm and Todoist will turn that into a task titled Complete new logo and add a due date of tomorrow at 2pm.\n\nYou can organize your tasks into projects and they can be shared with others for team collaboration on everything from school projects to software and gaming development. Tasks can include comments and be assigned to individual users making team collaboration easier.\n\nFiles can be uploaded from your computer, Dropbox, or Google Drive.\n\nTodoist can be deployed both in the cloud and on a local server and used across desktop and mobile devices.\n\nWhether you want to create a shopping list for your family or are working with your colleagues to launch the next viral app sensation, Todoist can make task management easier.","meta_title":"Todoist Alternatives | Taskade vs Todoist | Taskade","meta_description":"Taskade is a free Todoist alternative allowing you to easily manage your tasks and to-do lists. For personal or team collaboration. "},{"competitor_name":"Toggl Plan","slug":"free-toggl-plan-alternative","excerpt":"Taskade is the Toggl Plan alternative for Team Management","jumbotron_title":"Team Planning Made Simple","jumbotron_subtitle":"Chat, Organize, Get Things Done","competitor_price":"Paid","taskade_price":"Free","logo":"static_images/comparisons/toggl-plan.png","feature_sections":[{"features":[{"name":"The Visual Playground","tooltip_text":"Availability of templates and their ease of use.","competitor_offering":"Develop Gantt chart orientated templates","taskade_offering":"Develop customizable templates"},{"name":"Own Your Workspace","taskade_offering":"Fully customizable workspace and progress track